Ended 2022 with a
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀BIG DISNEY KISS GOODBYE 🥂
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
2022 taught me to just go for it
✍🏼 Signed a lease to open my own salon space, gutted the entire place & made it my own
🎫 bought a ticket for the biggest hair show not knowing my photo would be nominated in the top 200 in a category of over 37,000 other amazing hair photos
🔖 Booked the biggest, most magical vacation trip for my family and made the best memories
🎢 went on the fearfall ride with my teenager and faced a fear of hights just for her lol 😱😩
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
You just never know what tomorrow will bring, life could be taken away from you in a blink of an eye.
Buy the ticket, take the trip, go on the ride, make the memories, live life cuz tomorrow is never promised
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Go for it, make the slips and the falls, brush yourself off and get back to it!
Make the memories, I wanna enjoy all the moments with my kids while I can when their little.
When in doubt, Take. The. Photo. cuz one day you will look back with a warm heart and say ‘remember when we did this?!’ and laugh in aww about it.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Seeing how much my kids and I have grown in a year is crazy (I’m a mom of a teenager!!?? Like when did that happen??) i wish time would slow down but I love seeing them grow into their goofy selves (especially the teenager 😆)
Thankful for this device in my hand that is able to capture so many daily memories right at my fingertips…. But still figuring out places to back them onto 🫠
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Thank you @disney  @universalorlando  and @etfamilytravel for the magical experience,
it was all I dreamed of and more for my family 🧚🏼

➖Color Correction➖
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
New babe here, came in with a beautiful blonde but her roots were smudged with the wrong tone.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
When root tapping, smudging or melting you want to make sure the color is similar to the clients natural tone, so that way when the hair grows out it’s a seamless blend
When in doubt use a neutral, a gold & an ash.
In between her foils I smudged her roots using @redken #shadeseq 05n 06nb 04na
Toned her with 09n 09gb 09nb
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Hope this was helpful to anyone who needed it 🫶🏻

HOW TO: DIY Christmas Photo Shoot
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
𝑾𝒊𝒕𝒉 𝒂 𝒅𝒐𝒈:
We’ve learned with a dog the key is to stay calm and don’t move too quickly.
With having us all outside, Prince thought it was a play date lol but as soon as he saw the kids sit down on the set up he went right to it and laid on the blanket. He a funny boy but very high energy at times.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
𝑾𝒊𝒕𝒉 3 𝒌𝒊𝒅𝒔:
I prepared my kids for this day and time, days ahead. They knew Saturday at 1:00 we’re taking Christmas photos. So they were prepared and knew what to wear. They knew I wanted Prince to be in the picture so it would take some patience and a bit of time.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
𝑷𝒓𝒐𝒑𝒔:
Our back drop it our very old fence in the back yard, a few hanging decor made it not look so bad. Blankets and pillows to make it look cozy and I took Ray Ray’s Christmas tree from @fivebelow (that we just decorated a day or two before this lol) took the ornaments off and just put a bow on it to keep it simple.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
𝑪𝒂𝒎𝒆𝒓𝒂:
You need something fast when you’re working with a dog and 3 kids. iPhone never really does it for me so I used my cannon, it snaps a lot of photos pretty fast and clear.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Most of all make it fun, take some bloopers, make them laugh and cherish the moment 🫶🏻
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

family photo shoot 📸
